verbose_text: We further confirmed that the basal protein expression levels of VCAM1 and ICAM1 in the RCAs of APPsw mice were much higher than those of non Tg mice, consistent with the mRNA expression levels shown in Figure XREF_FIG A, and that the expression level changes in APPsw-Tg mice LCAs compared with RCA were much greater than those in non Tg mice.
